Published on Jul 16, 2015WHAT DOES GLOBAL MEAN FOR MASTERCARD?full story: http://insights.som.yale.edu/insights...Does being a global company mean being the same everywhere, or adapting to local customs and business environments? In an interview with Yale Insights, MasterCard CEO Ajay Banga says that the company succeeds because it has a single global product, but draws strength from the diversity of its workforce around the world. 



